# <type>(<scope>): <summary>
# A blank line followed by a detailed description (optional)
# BREAKING CHANGES on another line (optional)
# Common type types:
# feat New feature
# fix Fix bugs
# docs Document changes
# style style/format
# refactor Refactoring, no feature changes
# test test
# chore Miscellaneous items such as build configuration
# build Build-related
# ci CI/CD changes
# revert Rollback
# Example (supports multiple scopes):
# feat(api,ui): add user permission editor
# build
# Add user permission editor function, support permission selection and rollback.
#
# BREAKING CHANGE: user permission structure changed
